data.name: textBox1.Text
data.value:
Rules: - game must be in Windowed or Borderless Windowed mode - UI: set scale to 100%, use dark scheme - npc must be selected - capture during Blue turn, after all card animations finished (!!!)
Multi monitor setup notes: - moving overlay between monitors can cause it to disappear, toggle off and on again to restore - overlay will position itself every time it's shown (if game is already running) or capturing
Works with Mini Cactpot too :D
